# HustleMode.ai Architecture

## Core Principles
- Stateless, prompt-based workflow
- Azure AI Studio (Foundry) for orchestration
- Public API endpoints for integration
- Future extensibility for messaging channels

## Architecture Components

### 1. Prompt Layer
- Centralized prompt management
- Version-controlled prompt templates
- Environment-specific configurations

### 2. AI Orchestration
- Azure AI Studio (Foundry) integration
- Flow management and routing
- Response processing and formatting

### 3. API Layer
- RESTful endpoints
- Stateless request handling
- Standardized response formats

### 4. Integration Points
- WhatsApp (future)
- SMS (future)
- Email (future)

## Development Guidelines

### Code Organization
- Keep prompts in dedicated directories
- Maintain clear separation of concerns
- Document all API endpoints
- Version all prompts and flows

### Testing
- Unit test all prompt variations
- Integration test API endpoints
- Load test for concurrent requests

### Security
- API key management
- Rate limiting
- Input validation
- Response sanitization

### Documentation
- API documentation
- Prompt templates
- Flow diagrams
- Integration guides
